'''Broken Mirror''' ni filimi yo muri [[Gana]]  yasohotse muri 2014 ikozwe na  Media 5 Studio Productions. James Gardiner, Fred Amugi, Jackie Appiah, Roselyn Ngissah, Mikki Osei Berko, Victoria Lebene Mekpah na Jasmine Baroudi ni abakinnyi bingenzi. Yanditswe na Pappa Deric kandi yakozwe na David Owusu hamwe na Mikki Osei Berko nk'umuyobozi. Ninkuru yumugore uhinda umushyitsi mugihe amahirwe y'umukunzi we ahindutse neza, nyuma yo kumuhagararaho mubihe bikomeye. 

== Umugambi ==
Thompson yakinnye na James Gardiner, ni umunyeshuri urangije kaminuza udafite akazi ufata ububaji kugira ngo abeho. Umukunzi we Priscilla ( Jackie Appiah ) yamuhaye inkunga y'amarangamutima ndetse n'amafaranga. Priscilla udakize kandi akora akazi ko kudoda, ahora ashimishwa na bagenzi be Evelyn (Roselyn Ngissah) na Angela (Victoria Lebene Mekpah) kubera urukundo rwe no gushyigikira byimazeyo Thompson. Kumwizera kumutsindira mugihe cyImana birakomeye kandi arabikora mugihe cy'umwaka.

Barashyingirwa, barishima kandi bategereje umwana wabo wambere, mugihe Thompson yakiriye amashusho yerekana Priscilla nundi mugabo. Ibi bimuha kumva ko ariganya kandi biganisha ku gusenyuka. Evelyn amenyesha umukunzi we Priscilla mugihe runaka. Hari ukuntu yemera ko Priscilla yamwibye kandi niwe uri ku mashusho hamwe na we.
